{"title":"乡间","authors":["赵贵辰"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":2,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵贵辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用那警句般的眼睛看我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用那歌曲般的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤我。我光着脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柔柔地穿着你的厚爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次次从田野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抒情而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用那茧手拉着我的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茧手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用那汗水喂养我的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水。我赤着双足"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腾腾地走过你走过的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小路，一步步的拔节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱你的一切：爱你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纺织黎明的夜晚，爱你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹拨岁月的炊烟，爱你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲刷忧愁的泪水，爱你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑容流淌的褶皱，爱你……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是一部刊在大地上的史诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我研墨吟写你时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是多么心跳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一笔一画全是我的自豪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一片神奇的土地啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收获的姐妹们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦穗儿与麦穗儿跳起交际舞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野长熟了汗珠子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她拿着镰刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同姐妹们那放开四蹄的歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块儿来到田埂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有比这更快活的事了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳欣赏着她们的脸蛋儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且要火辣辣的吻黑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随便，姐妹们抛弃羞意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猫下腰以裸露的臂膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向远方拥去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦茬儿在转眼的工夫短了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小蚂蚱蹦跳在那里，寻觅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知为什么丢了的森林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹们回头一瞥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傍晚的炊烟跑出了村庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把镰刀杆儿夹在胳肢窝儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后走过井台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让凉水冲淡一肚子闷热"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}